subproject.description:
Northern State Government and Federal Ministry Staff responsible for planning and budgeting trained in planning, budgeting and performance monitoring methodologies.
Delivery of the 2008 budget submissions for Northern States and Federal Ministries aligned with the NSP inputs and approved;
Approved strategy for incorporating Southern Sudan working plans into the NSP;
Approved 2008 NSP submissions from Southern States and the GOSS;
Approved 2008 NSP revision linked to budget forecasts;
2008 budget forecasts reflecting priorities of NSP;
Raise Awareness of the NSP in State Governments and Federal Ministries;
Monitoring and evaluation plan for the NSP at the sector, federal ministry and state level approved; and
NSP documents translated into English.
